// Exact trail counts for the behavior table, pinned per pattern.
//
// Each row is the number of distinct trails the checker emits for a pattern
// under `max_score = inf, max_steps = 5000`. The conformance test asserts the
// checker produces exactly this many trails. A change to trail enumeration or
// score that does not flip the safe/unsafe verdict still shifts these counts,
// so this table catches drift the verdict-only checks miss.
//
// Do not edit by hand.

